parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering flexible coupler can cause the steering wheel to seize, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Clicking
clunking
or thudding noise when turning the steering wheel
feeling of play or looseness in the steering wheel
pulling or resistance when turning
difficulty steering
and loss of control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause loss of steering assist, making it difficult to control the vehicle, leading to accidents and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Loss of power steering assist
difficulty steering
EPS and Traction Control lights illuminated
and abnormal noises or vibrations when steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag Warning Light and Electrical Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system and electrical issues can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities due to the lack of airbag deployment or electrical fires.
symptoms: Airbag warning light illuminated
electrical issues
and burning smell or smoke from the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hydraulic brake system can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to increased stopping distances, accidents, or even fires, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake fluid leaks
ABS warning light illumination
traction control warning light illumination
smoke or fire from the engine compartment
unusual odors
stalling
and airbag warning light illumination.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of parts to repair the hydraulic brake system can leave vehicles in an unsafe condition, increasing the risk of accidents or fires.
symptoms: Notification of recall
but parts are not available for repair
exceeding a reasonable amount of time for recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the non-deployment of airbags in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag light comes on intermittently
the airbag light stays on constantly
the airbag system malfunction warning is displayed on the dashboard
the airbag system fails to deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the vehicle is unable to slow down or stop
the brake warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system issues can cause various safety-related problems, including airbag system malfunctions and brake system failures.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on intermittently
the brake light is illuminated
the steering wheel clicks when turning
the engine light is on
the tire pressure sensor light is always on.
